# Custom Filter Tests
## Strip Filter
Original: '  hello world  '
Stripped: 'hello world'
## Replace Filter
Original: foo bar foo baz foo
Replace all 'foo' with 'bar': bar bar bar baz bar
Replace first 'foo' with 'qux': qux bar foo baz foo
Replace two 'foo' with 'xyz': xyz bar xyz baz foo
## Replace Regex Filter
Original: test123abc456def789
Remove all digits: testabcdef
Replace digits with '#': test#abc#def#
Replace first digit sequence: testNUMabc456def789
Replace letters with '*': *123*456*789
## Chained Filters
Strip then replace: 'goodbye world'
Replace then strip: 'hello universe'
Complex chain: XXX XXX
## Multiline Strip
Multiline stripped: 'Line with spaces  
Another line'
